coza.opencollab.synthesis.service.api.util

Interface StorageEntryComparer


  • public interface StorageEntryComparer
    Compares two entry collections and return a collections of new entries.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    OpenCollab

    • Method Detail

      • diff

        List<StorageEntry> diff(List<StorageEntry> entriesA,
                      List<StorageEntry> entriesB)
        Compares the entries from entriesA to the entries from entriesB and retrieve the diff (new) entries from entriesB.
        Parameters:
        entriesA - A list of entries.
        entriesB - A list of entries.
        Returns:
        The entries that is new in entriesB. If there is entries that contain different data but are the same entry then entryB's data will be returned.

      • diffWithDelete

        List<StorageEntry> diffWithDelete(List<StorageEntry> entriesA,
                                List<StorageEntry> entriesB)
        Compares the entries from entriesA to the entries from entriesB and retrieve the diff (new) entries from entriesB.
        Parameters:
        entriesA - A list of entries.
        entriesB - A list of entries.
        Returns:
        The entries that is new in entriesB. If there is entries that contain different data but are the same entry then entryB's data will be returned. Also delete markers for entries that is not in entriesB anymore.

      • merge

        List<StorageEntry> merge(List<StorageEntry> baseEntries,
                       List<StorageEntry> newEntries)
        Merge the entries together. The values for newEntries will overwrite the values of baseEntries.
        Parameters:
        baseEntries - A list of entries that form the base.
        newEntries - A list of entries that will be added and overwrite the base.
        Returns:
        All the merged entries.
